---
import Layout from '../../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import digitalMarketingFront from '../../../assets/images/services/digital-marketing-front.png';
import digitalMarketingMiddle from '../../../assets/images/services/digital-marketing-middle.png';
import digitalMarketingBack from '../../../assets/images/services/digital-marketing-back.jpg';
import digitalMarketingOffice from '../../../assets/images/services/digital-marketing-office-photo.jpg';
---

<Layout title="Digital Marketing">
  <SimpleHero
    tagline="Services"
    title="Digital Marketing"
    description="Digital marketing works when the strategy is specific, the message is clear, and the next move is measurable. We build marketing systems around the real problem your business needs to solve."
    mediaFront={digitalMarketingFront}
    mediaFrontWidth={1300}
    mediaFrontHeight={1300}
    mediaMiddle={digitalMarketingMiddle}
    mediaMiddleWidth={1300}
    mediaMiddleHeight={1300}
    mediaBack={digitalMarketingBack}
    mediaBackWidth={1300}
    mediaBackHeight={1300}
  />
  <div class="service-intro service-intro--marketing">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <p class="h4">
        Most marketing problems are really diagnosis problems. If the audience is off, the message is vague, or the
        reporting does not lead to action, more activity will not fix it.
      </p>
      <div class="service-intro-media" data-lg-parallax="child">
        <div>
          <Picture
            src={digitalMarketingOffice}
            alt="Kelpers reviewing marketing analytics"
            loading="lazy"
            width={866}
            height={866}
            widths={[480, 720, 866]}
            sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw"
            inferSize
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-intro-text">
        <p>
          We start by identifying what is actually broken, then shape the strategy, execution, and reporting around a
          clearer goal. That is how campaigns become easier to improve over time instead of harder to explain.
        </p>
        <p>
          We can support your in-house team, take ownership of specific channels, or manage the full campaign rhythm for
          you depending on where the bottleneck really is.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="service-list services-list--marketing wrapper">
    <h2>Digital Marketing</h2>
    <div class="service-list-item">
      <div data-lg-parallax data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.2">
        <div
          class="service-list-item-square"
          style="background-color: var(--light-green)"
          data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        data-lg-parallax
        data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.4"
        data-lg-lottie="/animations/audience-targeting.json"
        data-lg-lottie-autoplay="true"
        data-lg-lottie-loop="true"
        data-lg-lottie-lazy="true"
        class="service-list-item-icon"
      >
      </div>
      <h3 class="h4"><a href="/services/audience-targeting/">Audience Targeting</a></h3>
      <p>
        Marketing gets expensive fast when you are talking to everyone. Audience targeting helps narrow the message to
        the people most likely to care and convert.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-list-item">
      <div data-lg-parallax data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.2">
        <div
          class="service-list-item-square"
          style="background-color: var(--light-green)"
          data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        data-lg-parallax
        data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.4"
        data-lg-lottie="/animations/campaign-management.json"
        data-lg-lottie-autoplay="true"
        data-lg-lottie-loop="true"
        data-lg-lottie-lazy="true"
        class="service-list-item-icon"
      >
      </div>
      <h3 class="h4"><a href="/services/campaign-management/">Campaign Management</a></h3>
      <p>
        Campaigns work better when the timeline, message, assets, and budget move in the same direction instead of
        fighting each other.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-list-item">
      <div data-lg-parallax data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.2">
        <div
          class="service-list-item-square"
          style="background-color: var(--light-green)"
          data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        data-lg-parallax
        data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.4"
        data-lg-lottie="/animations/social-ppc.json"
        data-lg-lottie-autoplay="true"
        data-lg-lottie-loop="true"
        data-lg-lottie-lazy="true"
        class="service-list-item-icon"
      >
      </div>
      <h3 class="h4"><a href="/services/social-ppc/">Social & PPC</a></h3>
      <p>
        Paid media only works when the targeting, creative, and landing experience support the same goal.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-list-item">
      <div data-lg-parallax data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.2">
        <div
          class="service-list-item-square"
          style="background-color: var(--light-green)"
          data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        data-lg-parallax
        data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.4"
        data-lg-lottie="/animations/reporting.json"
        data-lg-lottie-autoplay="true"
        data-lg-lottie-loop="true"
        data-lg-lottie-lazy="true"
        class="service-list-item-icon"
      >
      </div>
      <h3 class="h4"><a href="/services/reporting/">Reporting</a></h3>
      <p>Reporting should make the next decision clearer, not just give you more charts to stare at.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style lang="scss">
  .service-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin-bottom: 8rem;
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    h2 {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: none;
      margin-top: 8rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      @media (max-width: 767px) {
        margin-top: 5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
    }
    &-item {
      flex: 1 1 400px;
      position: relative;
      p {
        max-width: 50ch;
      }
      &-square {
        width: 103px;
        height: 103px;
        left: 0;
        z-index: -1;
        top: 0;
        background: var(--light-teal);
      }
      &-icon {
        display: block;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        max-width: 120px;
        max-height: 120px;
      }
    }
  }
  .service-intro {
    background: var(--lighter-teal);
    padding: 8rem 0;
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .wrapper {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem 3rem;
    }
    .h4 {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
      color: var(--purple);
      max-width: 52ch;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }
    &-media {
      flex: 1 1 400px;
    }
    &-text {
      flex: 1 1 400px;
      p {
        max-width: none;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
